h3. Summary
Confluence Site Import is failing to complete

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Generate a backup from the latest Confluence Server Version 5.8.15
# Perform *site import* on Confluence Cloud
# Import fails

h3. Expected Results
Confluence site is imported successfully

h3. Actual Results
Confluence site backup from the latest version of Confluence Server fails with the following error:
{code}
@4000000056352caf121cb224 2015-10-31 14:03:33,303 ERROR [Long running task: Importing data] [confluence.util.longrunning.ConfluenceAbstractLongRunningTask] run Long running task "Importing data" failed to run.
@4000000056352caf121cb9f4  -- referer: https://example.atlassian.net/wiki/admin/import/importconfluencesite.action | url: /wiki/admin/import/doimportconfluencesite.action | userName: sysadmin | action: doimportconfluencesite
@4000000056352caf121cbddc java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: com.atlassian.sal.api.net.Request.addBasicAuthentication(Ljava/lang/String;Ljava/lang/String;)Lcom/atlassian/sal/api/net/Request;
@4000000056352caf121cd164       at com.atlassian.ondemand.backupmanager.client.DefaultCrowdUsersProvider.prepareCrowdPutRequest(DefaultCrowdUsersProvider.java:227)
@4000000056352caf121cd54c       at com.atlassian.ondemand.backupmanager.client.DefaultCrowdUsersProvider.setUserEncryptedPasswords(DefaultCrowdUsersProvider.java:148)
@4000000056352caf121cd934       at com.atlassian.ondemand.confluenceimporter.procesors.post.UserPostImportTask$1.run(UserPostImportTask.java:276)
{code}

h3.Workaround
Perform space by space import

h6.Steps to reproduce
# In a template (Global or Space), add the Page Properties macro and set it to 'Hidden';
# add a variable in the hidden macro;
# save the template;
# attempt to create a page from the template.

*Expected result:* the hidden macro is displayed in the 'Step 2: Fill in template variables' screen, and the page content created from template can be edited in the next step.
*Actual result:* in the 'Step 2: Fill in template variables' screen the hidden macro isn't displayed and the variable cannot be edited. In the next step, no page content is added from the template - the editor is empty.

h6.Workaround
Don't set the Page Properties macro to 'Hidden' in the template. Change the macro property before saving the new page created from template.
